    <title>formatting on vscode</title>
    <url>/2022/06/29/formatting-on-vscode/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="eslint和prettier"><a href="#eslint和prettier" class="headerlink" title="eslint和prettier"></a>eslint和prettier</h1><p>本文给出一个可行的解决eslint和prettier同时生效的vscode的解决方案。</p>
<h2 id="安装流程"><a href="#安装流程" class="headerlink" title="安装流程"></a>安装流程</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yarn add eslint prettier eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier -D </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// 生成.eslintrc.js，并根据选项下载对应的包</span><br><span class="line">npx eslint --init </span><br><span class="line">    eslint somename.js --fix // 原理：执行格式化脚本命令进行格式化</span><br><span class="line">//eslint插件安装</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    npx prettier --write index.js // 原理：脚本格式化</span><br><span class="line">.prettierrc.js //手动创建</span><br><span class="line">//prettier插件安装</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//eslint-config-prettier 的作用是关闭eslint中与prettier相互冲突的规则。</span><br><span class="line">//eslint-plugin-prettier 的作用是赋予eslint用prettier格式化代码的能力</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="配置文件"><a href="#配置文件" class="headerlink" title="配置文件"></a>配置文件</h2><h3 id="setting-json"><a href="#setting-json" class="headerlink" title="setting.json"></a>setting.json</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;editor.formatOnSave&quot;: true,</span><br><span class="line">  // 配置prettier为默认格式化工具，以vue为例</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;[vue]&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;editor.defaultFormatter&quot;: &quot;esbenp.prettier-vscode&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;editor.codeActionsOnSave&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;source.fixAll.eslint&quot;: true</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  // 配置 ESLint 检查的文件类型</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;eslint.validate&quot;: [</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;javascript&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;vue&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;html&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="eslintrc-js"><a href="#eslintrc-js" class="headerlink" title=".eslintrc.js"></a>.eslintrc.js</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    extends: [</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;plugin:prettier/recommended&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000015315545">https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000015315545</a><br><a href="https://juejin.cn/post/6990929456382607374">https://juejin.cn/post/6990929456382607374</a><br><a href="https://juejin.cn/post/7012160233061482532">https://juejin.cn/post/7012160233061482532</a></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
